This is an index of scenarios for "The Sands of War" and its Expansion
Kit.  For  each scenario,  you  will  find  which advanced  rules  are
necessary to play the scenario. So, for example, if you want to play a
scenario with helicopters,  you will immediately find  at first glance
the 12 scenarios which use helicopters.
